        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model form acceptance criteria — constitutive and contact fidelity",
        "description": "Bilinear isotropic hardening material model for Ti-6Al-4V must reproduce tensile coupon stress-strain to within 3% of published ASTM data; Augmented Lagrange contact must not exhibit spurious penetration >0.01 mm. Achieved: material calibration error <1.8%; maximum contact penetration 0.003 mm across all load steps."
      },
